			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64712938">		
		on Friday August 16, 2024 @09:56PM (<span class="ind"></span><a rel="nofollow" href="//yro.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23424808&amp;cid=64712938">#64712938</a>)
		<small> </small>
